thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F112116_cfc33f28f689de18b7a408c3d3a52ef3.jpg&h=7673ec6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/112116_6577d582f9a05dc8685cc7c9daf879de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F112116_6577d582f9a05dc8685cc7c9daf879de.jpg&h=e2cb40c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/112116_4b2facd2335c4f3b37d0cfdad8f51411.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F112116_4b2facd2335c4f3b37d0cfdad8f51411.jpg&h=cd27f801&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/112117_fba370976aadd40d8575b40bb874052a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F112117_fba370976aadd40d8575b40bb874052a.jpg&h=ab7914d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T14:13:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VMCzpkB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVMCzpkB.png&h=15fcfd3e&s={SIZE}\" /> 獨民不分"},{"pid":"607fa2867ffcb59e8bf837570698ce95da7d3e76","tid":1803870,"uid":169497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T14:40:25.000Z","msg":"希望大家真係客觀討論<br />\n唔好一句宜家講港獨言之尚早就車埋嚟<br />\n無論係食物食水資源 經濟能力<br />\n香港絕對有資格獨立 唔需要依賴中國<br />\n因為本身都無靠佢地<br />\n<br />\n只要政府唔奶共 事事以本土利益置上<br />\n推返海水化淡 就唔使買東江水<br />\n<br />\n旅遊業可以base on返香港特有文化特色<br />\n以香港嘅歷史背景<br />\n香港可以係鬼佬眼中最值得去嘅亞洲城市(國家）<br />\n唔使靠自由行金鋪藥房<br />\n<br />\n好似韓國咁大力推電影業<br />\n班電影唔使奶共奶大陸市場都可以自由創作<br />\n做返自己 唔使俾濕鳩合拍片規條綁手綁腳<br />\n未必返到當年咁輝煌 但係起碼係正宗港產片 <br />\n做返香港特色<br />\n<br />\n政府一日唔以本土長遠利益置上<br />\n香港依個城市(國家)就唔會有好嘅發展<br />\n<br />\n獨立唔係必須<br />\n但係獨立最可以確保政府係以本土長遠利益置上"},{"pid":"41b34417db639fdb22b92e53bb8a2525bc9a6135","tid":1803870,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"242145f415f8be70504681b7832498e40077589e","tid":1803870,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f086f90ae905ce8bcb34d38e888ba63865a939b7","tid":1803870,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T14:02:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/112115_83cc8a6f8fb02c3e0548fc7f0f694fad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F112115_83cc8a6f8fb02c3e0548fc7f0f694fad.jpg&h=264da00f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/112115_fc0954a4467495063a82d161a834a294.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F112115_fc0954a4467495063a82d161a834a294.jpg&h=29b47661&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/112116_cfc33f28f689de18b7a408c3d3a52ef3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F112116_cfc33f28f689de18b7a408c3d3a52ef3.jpg&h=7673ec6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/112116_6577d582f9a05dc8685cc7c9daf879de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F112116_6577d582f9a05dc8685cc7c9daf879de.jpg&h=e2cb40c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/112116_4b2facd2335c4f3b37d0cfdad8f51411.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F112116_4b2facd2335c4f3b37d0cfdad8f51411.jpg&h=cd27f801&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/112117_fba370976aadd40d8575b40bb874052a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F112117_f